Include /etc/ssh/sshd_config.d/*.conf
PermitEmptyPasswords yes
KbdInteractiveAuthentication no
UsePAM yes
X11Forwarding yes
PrintMotd no
AcceptEnv LANG LC_*

Subsystem       sftp    /usr/lib/openssh/sftp-server

Match User ssh
    ForceCommand /usr/local/bin/sshim.sh
    AllowTcpForwarding no
    X11Forwarding no
    PermitTTY no
